snippet.title: Weapon Hacker - Release Trailer - Steam
snippet.description:
A roguelite metroidvania where you hack scavenged parts into custom-made weapons and explore / shred your way through a multiverse of infested weapon facilities.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1090060/Weapon_Hacker/
Website: https://weaponhacker.com/
